<PageTitle>My Sales Order Management App</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to the Sales Order Management Application</h1>

<p>This application allows you to manage sales orders, windows, and sub-elements directly from a web interface, with data stored in a database. Here's what you can do:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>View Sales Orders:</strong> Browse all sales orders stored in the database.</li>
    <li><strong>Create New Orders:</strong> Add new sales orders with specific details.</li>
    <li><strong>Edit Orders:</strong> Change and save data for existing orders, including their state, name, and dimensions.</li>
    <li><strong>Delete Orders:</strong> Remove orders from the database.</li>
    <li><strong>Manage Windows:</strong> Each order can have multiple windows. Add, edit, and delete windows associated with any order.</li>
    <li><strong>Manage Sub-Elements:</strong> Manage the individual elements that make up each window.</li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to reach out.</p>

<p><em>Enjoy managing your sales orders effectively!</em></p>
